# Con-form Dashboard - Environment Variables

# ============================================
# SUPABASE CONFIGURATION (Required for Frontend)
# ============================================
# Your Supabase project URL
# Format: https://[project-id].supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://ibqgwakjmsnjtvwpkdns.supabase.co

# Your Supabase anonymous/public key
# This is safe to expose in the browser
VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key_here

# ============================================
# MCP (Model Context Protocol) CONFIGURATION
# ============================================
# Supabase Service Role Key (for MCP server - KEEP SECURE!)
# This is used by the MCP server to interact with Supabase from AI assistants
# Get from: https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/ibqgwakjmsnjtvwpkdns/settings/api
# IMPORTANT: This key has admin privileges - set as system environment variable
# NEVER commit this to .env or expose it in the browser
# See MCP_SETUP.md for detailed setup instructions
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_service_role_key_here

# ============================================
# ODOO CONFIGURATION (Required for Backend)
# ============================================
# These variables are configured in Supabase Edge Functions
# Go to: Supabase Dashboard > Edge Functions > Secrets
#
# Your Odoo instance URL (without trailing slash)
# ODOO_URL=https://your-company.odoo.com
#
# Odoo login username (email)
# ODOO_USERNAME=your.email@company.com
#
# Odoo login password
# ODOO_PASSWORD=your_secure_password
#
# Odoo API Key (if using API authentication instead of password)
# ODOO_API_KEY=your_api_key

# ============================================
# DEVELOPMENT NOTES
# ============================================
# 1. Copy this file to .env in the project root
# 2. Replace placeholder values with your actual credentials
# 3. Never commit .env to version control
# 4. Get Supabase credentials from: https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/ibqgwakjmsnjtvwpkdns/settings/api
# 5. Configure Odoo credentials in Supabase Dashboard under Edge Functions > Secrets

